  "title": "Department Store Sales Promoter | Little India ( 1 Year Contract) - YZ11",
  "description": "<p><strong>Position title: Sales Promoter (1 yr contract)</strong><br /> Location: Little India<br />Working days: 6 days per week, 1 weekday off<br />Working hours: 1pm – 10pm (1 hr meal break) <br /><strong>Salary : </strong>$1,500 basic + Incentive $400 + Commission (0.5 to 5%) = Gross possible up to $2400-2500<br /></p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><p>Listening and understanding customers’ needs, assist them to find the perfect product for their needs.</p></li><li><p>Constantly building product knowledge and delivering this knowledge in engaging ways.</p></li><li><p>Setting up attractive product displays and promotional booths.</p></li><li><p>Delivering presentations and demonstrations to customers and other stakeholders.</p></li><li><p>Distributing samples and providing feedback for improvement to the management team.</p></li><li><p>Following up with customers and providing guidance on product selection.</p></li><li><p>Meeting daily targets and submitting sales reports.</p></li><li><p>Networking with relevant stakeholders.</p></li><li><p>Searching for new business opportunities.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><p>Experience in promoting FMCG/OTC products in chain pharmacies and departmental stores</p></li><li><p>Retailer experience, will be a plus as well – this is for our merchandising and inventory management requirement, which is part and parcel of a promoter role as well</p></li><li><p>Preferable with experience in retail <br /></p><p><br /></p></li></ul><p>Tan Yen Zhen (Chen Yan Zhen) Reg No: R25138932</p><p>The SupremeHR Advisory Pte Ltd EA No: 14C7279</p><p><br />\n\n</p>",
